In [404]:
y_train=y_train.reshape((len(y_train),1))
y_test=y_test.reshape((len(y_test),1))

y=y.reshape((x.shape[0],1))
w=np.zeros((x.shape[1],1))
b=0

def hypothesis(x,w,b):
    h=np.dot(x,w)+b
    return h
def accuracy(x,y,w,b):
    h=hypothesis(x,w,b)
    acc=1-(np.sum(np.square(h-y))/np.sum(np.square(y-y.mean())))
    return acc

def compute_cost(x,y,w,b):
    h=hypothesis(x,w,b)
    m = len(y) 
    cost=(1/(2*m))*(np.sum(np.square(h-y)))
    return cost

def grad(x,y,w,b,lamda):
    m=y.shape[0]
    h=hypothesis(x,w,b)
    db = (1/m) * np.sum(h - y)
    dw = ((1/m) * np.dot(x.T,(h-y)))+(lamda/m)*w
    return dw,db
def descent(x,y,alpha,iters,lamda,w,b):
    acc_hist=[]
    for i in range(iters+1):
        dw,db=grad(x,y,w,b,lamda)
        w=w-alpha*dw
        b=b-alpha*db
        #cost=compute_cost(x,y,w,b)
        acc=accuracy(x,y,w,b)
        acc_hist.append(acc*100)
        if(i%1000==0):
            print(str(i)+" =","{0:.2f}".format(acc*100))
    return w,b,acc_hist
